4.	 Any other requirements established by the Federal Law on Protection of Personal Data Held by Private Parties and/or other applicable laws.
At any time, the Contractor may request to suspend or cancel the sending of messages or commercial and new product information notices, via our Privacy Department.
If you request the correction of personal data should further indicate changes to be made and provide documentation to support your request.
The answer to your request will be communicated within 10 (ten) working days from the date the application was received, 5 (ﬁve) days may in cases where the law so provides; to the effect that if found appropriate, the necessary steps to comply with your request measures, which are being conducted within 15 (ﬁfteen) working days from the date on which it is communicated to the Contractor shall carry out the response to your request.
