In the event that information sent either electronically, Aeroenlaces Nacionales, S.A. de C.V., will require an email.
When personal data are no longer required to fulfill the purposes set out in this Privacy Notice and with applicable laws, shall be canceled, blocked, and deleted by operation of law.
The request is not valid with the omission of what is stated above.
